a.title: ― Command: Provides the following information on the command: The content of the command and the programming language used.

a.title: ― CommandFile: Identifies and provides a link to an external copy of the command, for example, a SAS Command Code script. Designates the programming language of the command file, a description of the location of the file , and a URN or URL for the command file.
